    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A high-grade white cardboard, supercalendered with China clay; also made by pasting together sheets of heavy ledger paper.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
